   <div class="teaser_fmt"> 
    <h3>Epilepsy Overview</h3> 
    <p>Epilepsy is a group of related disorders characterized by a tendency for recurrent seizures. There are different types of epilepsy and seizures. Epilepsy drugs are prescribed to control seizures, and rarely surgery is necessary if medications are ineffective.</p> 
